  1. Article Category(target) Article Title
    • link link url
    • DataFrame
    • null
    • save txt file --> target
    • get link in each title news link url
    • list
    • DataFrame save to txt file and csv file -> , ,

ดึงชื่อ link ในเเต่ละเดือน¶

In [4]:
# 
link_months = soup.find_all('a') #  tag a
link_month = [] 
for link in link_months: #  tag a
    if 'href' in link.attrs: #   tag a  href  href  list link_month  
        link_month.append(link.attrs['href'])
#         print(str(link.attrs['href']))

#   3  
for i in range(-3,0):
    link_month.pop(i)
link_month #  link

for link in link_month: # 
    
    #  link   
    link = (f'http://www.it.kmitl.ac.th/~teerapong/news_archive/{link}') 
    
    link_months.append(link) # link url  link_months
print(link_months)

1 เริ่มจากการดึงข้อมูล target เเละ หัวข้อข่าว¶

  • link url list categorical (target)
In [7]:
res = [] # 
for link in link_months: #  
        response = requests.get(link) # 
        soup = bs4.BeautifulSoup(response.content) #  bs4  get  

        table = soup.find('table') # 
        tbody = table.find('tbody') #   tbody tag
        table_rows = tbody.find_all('tr') # tr  tbody   tag tr --> td 
        for tr in table_rows: # 
            td = tr.find_all('td') # return  tag td  
            row = [tr.text.strip() for tr in td]#    target    row
            if row: #  row 
                res.append(row) #  append  list res 
        print(res) #

2. เก็บข้อมูล content เเละหัวข้อของข่าว¶

  • get name link in each title news content link -

    In [13]:
    # Get all name link 
link_url = []
for month in link_month:  #  link month  12 link 
    response1 = requests.get(f'http://www.it.kmitl.ac.th/~teerapong/news_archive/{month}') #  link 
#     print(response1)
    soup = bs4.BeautifulSoup(response1.content, 'lxml')
    getlink = soup.find_all('a') #  tag a  tag a  link 
    for link in getlink: #  tag a  
        if 'href' in link.attrs: #  attribute href  tag a  append  href  list link_url
            link_url.append(link.attrs['href'])
            
#     
    for i in range(-4,0,1): #  4   '#'  index.html  link  
        link_url.pop(i) # 
#     len(listlinks) # 
print(link_url) #  link     
len(link_url)

      ขั้นตอนการเก็บหัวข้อข่าวเเละเนื้อหาข่าวไว้ใน list เดียวกัน¶

      ตั้งฟังก์ชั่นเพื่อ return เฉพาะหัวข้อ¶

      In [17]:
      #  return  
def extract_title(soup): 
    selector = 'div.main > h2'   #  tag h2
    tag = soup.select_one(selector)
    title = tag.text # get text  tag h2 
    return title

      ตั้งฟังก์ชั่น เพื่อ return เนื้อหาข่าว¶

      In [18]:
      def extract_body(soup):
    selector = 'div.main > p'
    tags = soup.select(selector)  #   tag p 
    data = []
    for tag in tags:  #  tag p
        dat = tag.get_text(strip=True)  #     
        data.append(dat) #   list data 
    data = " ".join(data) #   list    join    
    return data
      In [19]:
      # print(extract_body(soup))

      ฟังก์ชั่น สำหรับรวมเนื้อหาเเละหัวข้อมาในเเต่ละหน้าเว็บ¶

      In [20]:
      # content = [] # 
def extract_news_info(url):
    response = requests.get(link) # 
    soup = bs4.BeautifulSoup(response.content) #
    
    title = extract_title(soup) #  fn 
    body = extract_body(soup) #  fn  
    
    bodies = [title , body] #  list 
    return bodies
      In [21]:
      #  
extract_news_info('http://www.it.kmitl.ac.th/~teerapong/news_archive/article-jan-4007.html')
      Out[21]:
      ['Zambia confident and cautious',
 ' Zambia\'s technical director, Kalusha Bwalya is confident and cautious ahead of the Cosafa Cup final against Angola on Saturday in Lusaka.  Bwalya said: "Nothing short of victory will do." However Bwalya warned his side not to be too complacent. "I don\'t want my team to be too comfortable or too sure of victory as it is going to be a difficult game. "For me the main aim of the game is to enjoy and to win." Zambia have shown their determination to win this final by recalling nine of their foreign-based players. However the 41 year-old Bwalya, who became the oldest player to appear in the competition when he played and scored against Mauritius, is uncertain whether he will take to the field or not. The Chipolopolo fans however are not being so cautious with a \'victory\' concert already scheduled for after the match featuring some of the country\'s top musicians. Both sides are hoping to win the competition for a record third time, and so keep the trophy for good. The Chipolopolo won the first two editions of the regional tournament for Southern African nations in 1997 and 1998. They were prevented from a third straight win by Angola who knocked out the Zambians at the semi-final stage in 1999. That victory for Angola also marked a first defeat in 14 years for Zambia at Lusaka\'s Independence stadium, where Saturday\'s game is being played.       # text clening ()
def clean_text(raw_document):
    
    # 
    for i in raw_document:
        raw_document = raw_document.strip("Return to article search results\n") # 
        raw_document = raw_document.replace("Comments are closed for this article.",'') # 

        return raw_document

      2. Tokenize and 3. lemmatize function นี้จะเป็นการเลือกคำจาก word (ตัดคำออก)เเละยังไว้ซึ่งความหมายของคำเเต่ละคำด้วย¶

      In [34]:
      # define the function
def lemma_tokenizer(text): #  function  stop word   lemma
    
    from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import CountVectorizer
    standard_tokenizer = CountVectorizer().build_tokenizer() #  token  word   token != word 
    
    tokens = standard_tokenizer(text) #  

    lemmatizer = nltk.stem.WordNetLemmatizer() #  WordNetLemmatizer  normal form of word
    lemma_tokens = [] # list 
    for token in tokens: #  token  
        lemma_tokens.append( lemmatizer.lemmatize(token)) #  tokens  Dictionary 
    return lemma_tokens

   k '''

folds = 5 #  k-fold = 5  

''' StratifiedKFold  crossvalidation  train  test
 shuffle=True  fold '''
skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=folds, shuffle = True, random_state = 42) 

knn_best = GridSearchCV(knn, parameters, cv=skf) #  parameter  gridsearch  
Knn2 = knn_best.fit(X_train2,y_train2)  # train  80:20 , 70:30
knn3 = knn_best.fit(X_train3,y_train3) 

print("Best param for test 20")
print(Knn2.best_params_ ) #  n 

print("Best param for test 30")
print(knn3.best_params_)

      Best param for test 20
{'metric': 'euclidean', 'n_neighbors': 45, 'weights': 'uniform'}
Best param for test 30
{'metric': 'euclidean', 'n_neighbors': 45, 'weights': 'uniform'}

      กำหนด parameter เพื่อหา best params ด้วย RandomizedSearchCV¶

      In [52]:
      ''' parameter  max depth  n_estimators  tree  tree   
  overfit '''
parameters = {
    'max_depth': range (2, 10, 2),
    'n_estimators': range(60, 220, 40), #  tree  acc 
}


xgb = XGBClassifier(learning_rate=0.02, objective='multi:softmax') #  objective  multiclass 
# cross validation 
folds = 5
skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=folds, shuffle = True)

#  parameter   n_iter  5  n_jobs  train  ,  verbose =  train model
randomxgb = RandomizedSearchCV(xgb, param_distributions=parameters, n_iter=5, n_jobs=2, cv=skf, verbose=3, random_state=42) 
xgb2 = randomxgb.fit(X_train2,y_train2) # train   80 20 
xgb3 = randomxgb.fit(X_train3,y_train3) # train   70 30 
print(xgb2.best_params_) 
print(xgb3.best_params_)

    • Logistic Regression

      • binary classification class multiclass-classification class class % class

      In [58]:
      # Grid search and cross validation
from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV
from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
params={"penalty":["l1","l2"], # l1 l2  euclidean or manhattan l1-norm or l2-norm
       'C': [0.001, 0.01, 0.1, 1, 10]}   #  c   c  fit model  overfitting  
LR=LogisticRegression() #  model
folds = 5
skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=folds, shuffle = True, random_state = 1001) #  cross val
LR_cv=GridSearchCV(LR,params,cv=skf) #  best params  gridsearch
LR_cv2 = LR_cv.fit(X_train2,y_train2) # train model 80 | 20
LR_cv3 = LR_cv.fit(X_train3,y_train3) #train model 70|30
print("tuned hpyerparameters :(best parameters) ",LR_cv2.best_params_)
print("tuned hpyerparameters :(best parameters) ",LR_cv3.best_params_)

      tuned hpyerparameters :(best parameters)  {'C': 10, 'penalty': 'l2'}
tuned hpyerparameters :(best parameters)  {'C': 10, 'penalty': 'l2'}

      from sklearn.neural_network import MLPClassifier
NN = MLPClassifier()
''' parameter  neural network  hidden layer  train '''
parameter = {
    'hidden_layer_sizes': [(50,50,50), (50,100,50), (100,)],
    'activation': ['relu','softmax'],
    'solver': ['sgd', 'adam'],
    'alpha': [0.0001, 0.05],
    'learning_rate': ['constant','adaptive'],
}
folds = 5
skf = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=folds, shuffle = True, random_state = 1001)
NNgrid = GridSearchCV(NN, parameter, n_jobs=-1, cv=skf) # Tune parameter 
NN2 = NNgrid.fit(X_train2, y_train2) # train  80 20 
NN3 = NNgrid.fit(X_train3, y_train3) # train  80 20 
print(NN2.best_params_) #  return  best params
print(NN3.best_params_)

    • ensembles with individual model best parameter classifier ensembles

      • In [132]:
      # ensemble with individual model  bestparamKNN ,xgb_bestparams , LR_bestparam, NNbestparam 
from sklearn.ensemble import VotingClassifier 
'''  best parameter   4 model  [knn, xgboost, logistic regression  neural network]  train
 ensemble   accuracy  '''
estimator = [('Knn',knn.set_params(**bestparamKNN) ),('xgb',xgb.set_params(**xgb_bestparams)),
             ('LR' ,LR.set_params(**LR_bestparam) ), ('NN' ,NN.set_params(**NNbestparam))] #  
#  voting  soft   4   hard  majority voting
ensemble = VotingClassifier(estimator,voting='soft') 
ensemble.fit(X_train2,y_train2) # fit  80 20    80 20  accuracy  
pred =ensemble.predict(X_test2) #  X_test 
accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test2, pred) #  model 
print("Ensemble model perform = {:.2f}%". format(accuracy*100))

      Ensemble model perform = 98.58%

      สรุป ค่า accuracy ของเเต่ละโมเดล ที่ได้จากการทดลอง¶
